{
  "stem": "24163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't-- we were-- we were not all that concerned, as far as-- certainly, our family was concerned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My dad always said, well, these movements, oh, they come and they go, like so many did during the Weimar Republic, which was the period after World War I.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One regime after another came and fell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they all thought this would be just a-- a glitch, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it turned out to be otherwise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, they were Social Democrats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- in 1933-- I'm tracing back-- was about the time when I might have transferred from the Jewish day school to the gymnasium that I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'd have to think about it for a minute. 1933-- no, I think I was already enrolled in the [GERMAN] at that time, in-- in Gelsenkirchen, yes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gentile boys that I had befriended, or the school-- my school chums, certainly showed an alienation towards all of us Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almost from the very beginning, they just fell in line with the rest of the German people, because Hitler, from day one, advocated an anti-Jewish trend.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and he-- his speeches all were anti-Semitic speeches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the general population followed him, like a-- you know, a bunch of sheep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the-- and the young people did the very same thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they called us names on the street and-- and picked fights with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got beaten up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even some of my closer Gentile friends just simply didn't associate was-- with-- with-- with us anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they stayed away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just-- That was the very first inclination or indication we had of what was about to happen to the rest of us in-- in the years to come.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
